ManageOutput

DataAnalysisJava is a first version of a data analysis package for Java. Class ManageOutput supports copy to clipboard, save to file (prompt dialog for file name), and print (print dialog) functionality from output display windows. Note: print not yet fully functional.

Version:
0.1, 2003-May-15
Author:
Fionn Murtagh, fmurtagh@acm.org
